{"tid":992314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］黃之峰衝入政總反國歌法","createTime":"2019-01-23T05:32:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T16:36:23.000Z","uid":20058,"like":99,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"c4832f6af041d5f700b87aba2600f5e6e7faa146","tid":992314,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T05:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40c2c586cb7bfc3d0025f7224d53f915c9de7d6a","tid":992314,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T05:33:47.000Z","msg":"黃之*鋒"},{"pid":"d801bf98a97342d2b251723c327b11ee57d7d610","tid":992314,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T05:34:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/128807942654/posts/10156592736467655?sfns=st\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F128807942654%2Fposts%2F10156592736467655%3Fsfns%3Dst&d=tutJX9Q1VHv%2FYSiL6Mt37f755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=58afc90d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/128807942654/posts/10156592736467655?sfns=st</a>"},{"pid":"fef85bee50a97c196007abfa03705e077ef9b0d1","tid":992314,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32dfa080ddd4db0a3be72e32e859982f05320e1","tid":992314,"uid":79563,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190123/photo/bkn-20190123105415827-0123_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190123140432\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190123%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190123105415827-0123_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190123140432&h=9f38b390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《國歌條例草案》今日(23日)在立法會進行首讀及二讀，曾因為衝擊俗稱公民廣場的政府總部東翼前地而被判參與非法集會罪成的香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒，早上與香港眾志主席林朗彥、成員周庭等人，衝上政總東翼前地花槽上示威，反對國歌法立法，並與保安衝突。政府發言人強烈譴責香港眾志成員今早闖入政府總部東翼前地，指事件導致一名保安受傷，行政署已就事件報警，警方亦派員跟進調查。<br />\n<br />\n早上約10時，黃之鋒、林朗彥及周庭等人，帶同梯及橫額衝上花槽，保安立即要求他們離去，並衝上花槽阻止他們掛上橫額，雙方糾纏期間發生拉扯，又一度爭奪該幅橫額。林朗彥叫咪要求保安放手，保安就要求香港眾志的成員離開。香港眾志堅持把寫有「不歌頌的自由」橫額掛上花槽上的旗桿。<br />\n<br />\n林指，政府應中止國歌法立法程序，並公開諮詢市民，不要將國歌法刑事化。黃之鋒就指，選擇在該處掛起橫額，是因為政總東翼前地三米高圍欄所限制的自由，與國歌法限制的自由同出一轍，呼籲所有議員要求撤回國歌法。他們叫咪後離開花槽，整個行動維時約五六分鐘。保安員其後拆走該幅掛在旗桿的橫額。<br />\n<br />\n政府指，香港眾志成員今早闖入政府總部東翼前地，不理在場保安人員勸喻和警告，強行在旗桿平台掛上示威標語，並導致一名保安人員受傷及部分植物受到破壞。政府尊重市民表達意見的權利，但同時亦要保障政府總部的有效、安全、順利運作。一直以來，政府總部東翼前地旗桿平台並不屬於開放予公眾進行集會/遊行的範圍。"},{"pid":"1c66f07f68c5249e58f9641dcf7321fa0c3ba4d3","tid":992314,"uid":175623,"like":39,"dislike":2,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:26:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母班支那仔，建制派，焦土派話我地冇做野？cls<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b92156961c8f4b32c6eb583ca68dde9b42e1ae77","tid":992314,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3d4d0145260770d5644ea48cd35f1cb757a52e","tid":992314,"uid":47359,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"b92156961c8f4b32c6eb583ca68dde9b42e1ae77","tid":992314,"uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},